@2015 = ~The dark Lord Hertious, an undead warlord of Bane, wore this piece of armor over 500 years ago. It is rumored that he lived during that time in a castle somewhere in the Spine of the World. How his armor arrived without him in a different country is unknown, but the separation of the two was certainly not pleasant.

